import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';

function Cardu() {
  return (
    <>    <Card style={{ width: '12rem' }}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px180" />
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Egyes Téma</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Some sdadfsdafas
        </Card.Text>
        <Button variant="primary">Váltás</Button>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>

    <Card style={{ width: '12rem' }}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px180" />
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Egyes Téma</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Some sdadfsdafas
        </Card.Text>
        <Button variant="primary">Váltás</Button>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>

    <Card style={{ width: '12rem', position}}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px180" />
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Egyes Téma</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Some sdadfsdafas
        </Card.Text>
        <Button variant="primary">Váltás</Button>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
    </>
  );
}

export default Cardu;
